msg: Added user_logged_in and wait_for_logoff subroutines to Windows.pm and added call to wait_for_logoff to post_load. This causes the vcld process to wait for root's autoadminlogon scripts to finish before forcefully logging off root.
Also fixed bug in set_service_startup_mode where it was possible to try to print an uninitialized variable.
